Golbat (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0041: Zubat
Pokémon
#0043: Oddish →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Golbat (TCG Pocket).

Golbat has been featured on 23 different cards since it debuted in the Fossil expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Golbat cards are normally Darkness-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Golbat

Golbat
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
